Subject: [PATCH 01/53] feat(customized_vllm): add thread-local attention
 context module

Introduce Context dataclass and thread-local storage for passing attention
metadata between the inference engine and attention layers. Supports both
prefill mode (cu_seqlens_q/k, max_seqlen) and decode mode (slot_mapping,
context_lens, block_tables). Includes get_context(), set_context(), and
