Subject: [PATCH 02/53] feat(customized_vllm): add sequence state and block
 allocator

Implement Sequence class for tracking generation state (token_ids,
block_table, sampling params) and BlockAllocator for paged KV cache
block management. Supports CFG (classifier-free guidance) via paired_seq.
SequenceStatus enum (WAITING/RUNNING/FINISHED) and block boundary logic
for dynamic block allocation during decode.

Made-with: Cursor
