Subject: [PATCH 03/53] feat(customized_vllm): add SamplingParams and token
 sampler

Define SamplingParams dataclass (temperature, max_tokens, cfg_scale,
top_k, top_p, repetition_penalty, logits_processor). Implement Sampler
module with torch.compile for batched token sampling. Includes
_apply_top_k_top_p and _apply_top_k_only for nucleus/top-k filtering.
Validates sampling constraints in __post_init__.

Made-with: Cursor
