Subject: [PATCH 04/53] feat(customized_vllm): add RMSNorm, RoPE, and SiLU
 layers

Implement core neural network components: RMSNorm with optional fused
residual add (torch.compile), RotaryEmbedding (RoPE) with cached cos/sin,
and SiluAndMul for gated MLP. get_rope() provides cached RoPE instances.
Optimized for Qwen3 architecture compatibility.

