Subject: [PATCH 05/53] feat(customized_vllm): add paged KV cache attention
 with Flash/SDPA

Multi-head attention with paged KV cache. Triton kernel for fast cache
store; PyTorch fallback when Triton unavailable. Flash Attention for
prefill (varlen) and decode (with_kvcache) when installed; SDPA fallback
otherwise. Supports GQA. Integrates with thread-local context for
prefill/decode metadata.

