Subject: [PATCH 06/53] feat(customized_vllm): add safetensors loader with
 packed-module support

Load Qwen3 weights from safetensors with packed-module mapping (q/k/v
-> qkv_proj, gate/up -> gate_up_proj). _get_param resolves names with
and without 'model.' prefix. Supports custom weight_loader per parameter
for sharded loading. Handles multiple .safetensors files in model directory.

