Subject: [PATCH 29/53] refactor(customized_vllm): add InferencePipeline -
 execution and sampling layer

Introduce pipeline.py replacing runner.py with clearer separation of
concerns: model loading, KV cache provisioning, CUDA graph capture,
and forward execution.

SAMPLING:
- sample_tokens(): torch.compile'd temperature-scaled sampling with
  nucleus/top-k filtering. All params are tensors (never None) for
  stable torch.compile graph.
- _filter_by_top_k(), _filter_by_nucleus(): combined top-k and top-p.
  k=0 skips top-k, p=1.0 skips top-p.

INFERENCE PIPELINE:
- InferencePipeline: loads CausalTransformer, provisions KV cache,
  captures CUDA graphs for decode. Uses _xfer dict for pinned CPU
  buffers (temps, guidance, top_k, top_p, rep_pen, token_ids,
  positions, slots, ctx_lens).
- _init_transfer_buffers(): pre-allocate pinned buffers for GPU transfer.
- _warmup_pipeline(): dummy prefill, reset_context, empty_cache.
- _provision_kv_storage(): compute block count from gpu_memory_utilization,
  MAX_CUDA_VRAM env support. Assign k_cache/v_cache to attention layers.
- _build_cache_index(): block tables for decode.
- _execute_prefill(): packed sequences, cu_seqlens, slot_mapping,
  _set_forward_state(True, ...).
- _execute_autoregressive(): single-token decode, _set_forward_state(False).
- _forward_pass(): eager for prefill/large batch; CUDA graph replay for
  decode when block_tables/context_lens match.

SAMPLING HELPERS:
- _gather_sampling_config(): pack temps, cfg_scale, top_k, top_p, rep_pen.
  Always returns tensors for stable sample_tokens signature.
- _penalize_repetitions(): repetition penalty per slot.
- _constrain_logits(): logits processors, broadcast to batch.
- execute_step(): full forward + sampling, CFG support.
- _compile_execution_graphs(): capture CUDAGraphs for batch sizes
  [1,2,4,8,16,...,512].
- shutdown(): cleanup graphs, synchronize.

