Subject: [PATCH 50/53] fix(customized_vllm): pass block_size to warmup dummy
 slots in pipeline

Thread self.block_size into GenerationSlot during _warmup_pipeline so
dummy slot block calculations match the configured KV cache block size.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
---
 acestep/customized_vllm/pipeline.py | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/acestep/customized_vllm/pipeline.py b/acestep/customized_vllm/pipeline.py
