Subject: [PATCH 52/53] fix(customized_vllm): reject max_tokens <= 0 in
 SamplingParams validation

Without this check, max_tokens=0 or negative values would still emit
one token before _finalize_step enforces the stop condition, since
sampling runs before the length check.

